    AnyCharacterParser
    A parser which matches any character, resulting in that character.
    BinaryParser
    Parses a binary number from a bytes input.
    BytesParser

    CharacterParser
    A parser which matches a single character, resulting in that character if successful.
    ChoiceOfCharactersParser
    A parser which matches one of several characters, resulting in that character.

    A parser which matches the end of input.
    ExactBinaryParser
    Parses an exact binary number from a bytes input.
    RegexParser
    A parser which matches a regular expression in a string.
    StringParser
    A parser which matches a string, resulting in the input string if successful.
    TokensParser
    A parser which matches a sequence of tokens in a token list, based only on id (data is ignored).
